<view class="distributor">
    
   <view wx:if="{{ status === 0 }}">
        <view class="register-distributor" bind:tap="apply">
        分销商申请
        </view>
        <view class="rule-desc">
            申请成为分销商以后转发或者分享图片给其他客户,
            其他客户购买成功后则分销商享受订单的1%座位提成奖励，
            提成奖励将在7天后自动到账。
        </view>
   </view>
    <view class="reviewing" wx:elif="{{ status === 1 || status === 2 }}">
        <view class="header">
            <view class="title">
                {{ status === 1 ? '审核中...' : '申请失败' }}
            </view>
            <view class="desc">
                请随时关注本页面，等待审核完毕
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="rule-desc">
        申请成为分销商以后转发或者分享图片给其他客户,
        其他客户购买成功后则分销商享受订单的1%座位提成奖励，
        提成奖励将在7天后自动到账。
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="distribute-order-list" wx:else>
        <view class="tab">
            <view class="tab-item">
                订单id
            </view>
            <view class="tab-item">
                提成奖励
            </view>
            <view class="tab-item">
                是否发放
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="order-list">
            <view class="order-item" wx:for="{{ rewardList }}">
                <view class="order-item-item">{{ item.Id }}</view>
                <view class="order-item-item">{{ item.DistributionPrice }}</view>
                <view class="order-item-item">{{ item.DistributionStatus === 1 ? '未获取' : '已获取' }}</view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>